  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DId you ever dream to have a castle?<br><strong>Let's stand a castle on your computer's desktop!</strong></h2><br>It has a weather system that will be the SAME from your city. Sunny, cloudy, rainy, snowy... The weather will update every hour.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/ed5564fb46a1d46c9aae04a4f5daf08c.poster.avif?t=1635494503\" width=600 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/ed5564fb46a1d46c9aae04a4f5daf08c.webm?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/ed5564fb46a1d46c9aae04a4f5daf08c.mp4?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And the time of the castle is synchronize from real time of yours!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/77113fb9eb290ed51b44da1b779cb15c.poster.avif?t=1635494503\" width=600 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/77113fb9eb290ed51b44da1b779cb15c.webm?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/77113fb9eb290ed51b44da1b779cb15c.mp4?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fireworks every hour during night time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/f29ba155e8cf3a8438c7937042f518ea.poster.avif?t=1635494503\" width=600 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/f29ba155e8cf3a8438c7937042f518ea.webm?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/f29ba155e8cf3a8438c7937042f518ea.mp4?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A team of cavalry runs out from the castle every half hours. Where will they go?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/e94bc048497ad1ac6f77c67a05c745c3.poster.avif?t=1635494503\" width=600 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/e94bc048497ad1ac6f77c67a05c745c3.webm?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790580/extras/e94bc048497ad1ac6f77c67a05c745c3.mp4?t=1635494503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Melodious sound from bell tower every hour... And more features to be discovered! Have fun!",
